# Tacu Tacu

Based on [Cook Eat Live Love](https://cookeatlivelove.com/peruvian-vegetarian-tacu-tacu) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20251221035312/https://cookeatlivelove.com/peruvian-vegetarian-tacu-tacu/)) and [Goya](https://www.goya.com/en/recipes/tacu-tacu) ([wayback](http://web.archive.org/web/20260104013528/https://www.goya.com/en/recipes/tacu-tacu/))

